    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891700/extras/367321b4d1a22b56336d636531094ca7.poster.avif?t=1769636926\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891700/extras/367321b4d1a22b56336d636531094ca7.webm?t=1769636926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891700/extras/367321b4d1a22b56336d636531094ca7.mp4?t=1769636926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为忍者大师</h2>在这款增量游戏中，以忍者的身份开始你的冒险，找准时机用武士刀斩杀来袭的敌人，研究新的技术并建设你自己的村庄。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891700/extras/008127dd33f69af2265fce0b14ab4d68.poster.avif?t=1769636926\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891700/extras/008127dd33f69af2265fce0b14ab4d68.webm?t=1769636926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891700/extras/008127dd33f69af2265fce0b14ab4d68.mp4?t=1769636926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >招募并征服</h2>踏上由敌人管控的岛屿，建立自己的定居点。招募传奇英雄，派遣他们征服敌方行省，统一疆域。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891700/extras/b73066491b415d0ab7d20008c939a055.poster.avif?t=1769636926\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891700/extras/b73066491b415d0ab7d20008c939a055.webm?t=1769636926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891700/extras/b73066491b415d0ab7d20008c939a055.mp4?t=1769636926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集动物园</h2>收集并结交各种宠物，它们将在你的冒险中鼎力相助。与好友结伴，在旅途中增进你们之间的联系，让好友们变得更加强大。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>摧毁来袭的敌人，收集硬币，赚取金币<br></li><li>建立你的村庄，即使在离线状态下也能赚取更多金币！<br></li><li>购买研究升级以提高你的能力<br></li><li>提升并学习史诗和永久技能升级<br></li><li>收集宠物并用零食奖励它们<br></li><li>招募英雄并统一疆域<br></li><li>完美通关各种挑战<br></li><li>完成任务以获得奖励<br></li><li>解答每周谜语<br></li><li>解锁数百项成就<br></li><li>解锁角色并使用染色进行自定义<br></li><li>跨平台云存储——让你何时何地都可安心畅游！</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >未来路线图：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>更多升级和提升技能<br></li><li>更多成就<br></li><li>合成遗物<br></li><li>你自己的道场，可以自定义并展示所获成就<br></li><li>想提出建议？在Discord社群中分享</li></ul>",
